divs: sighting detailsthe place i work is under the landing path of o'hara airport the planes land and take off over our building they are very low when landing i have worked at this location for over 15 years i know the sound of airplanes\airport very well i herd a strange sound in the sky that i have herd before thru the years one of the other people also herd the sound last year with me i was leaving work i was facing south so to my left was east [ o'hara ] to my right was west i herd a strange woosh\swoosh sound with a dopler shift moving from east to west super fast in the sky ,but kind of low and loud enough to make you stop moving and look up i look up and see nothing the wind was very gentle, leaves hardley moving their was no sound before or after the event i have never herd this type of sound anywere before
